        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-08-09 21:49:03.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 8:\n\nI would suggest you change wrapper.sh to init.sh.\nentrypoint.sh to run_abrmd.sh\nThis way we can keep the same container image and run it in two different phases. \nFirst phase, we will run init.sh which runs run_abrmd.sh and initialize_tpm.sh and exit (you might have to remove the while loop in init.sh)\nSecond phase, we will run only run_abrmd.sh\nThe dockerfile itself does not need a default entrypoint/cmd",
        "patchset_number": 8
